{"tid":2159381,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"講吓心事 about 昔日女神","createTime":"2020-08-16T09:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T10:04:14.000Z","uid":366724,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f3bb43f7354803d81014f4cdc2930cd1b0ed78","tid":2159381,"uid":366724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:46:57.000Z","msg":"以前F.5-6 (exact時間唔講lu)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係我生日之前送咗份禮物俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n份禮物用 &lsquo; I love you &lsquo; 禮物紙包<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話佢冇晒禮物紙所以先會用<br />\n嗰陣信咗佢 冇咩點理<br />\n但係隔咗兩年突然諗返覺得好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個心仲係耿耿於懷 越諗越奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地覺得點解係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：自問屬於中中上男<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對我有極少好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />9uo咁都sense唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想玩下你咋 傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗佢應該唔會睇到掛掛掛～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHo Gang Gang <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adea48f1d00ad99b9daae6cb23b7a52a10576496","tid":2159381,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:53:40.000Z","msg":"有少少乸型嘅感覺"},{"pid":"5b0dd9b5f803d3bbd6bfca738638f3aa17720f67","tid":2159381,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:58:02.000Z","msg":"仲有無佢聯絡電話，直接打過去問丫嘛"},{"pid":"cb45dd67d36350c3657d099fed57af2bc32f78a9","tid":2159381,"uid":366724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor